    "description": "<p><strong>Save Enhancement:&nbsp;</strong>Target makes Physical Save against the chosen effect. If you spend <strong>AP </strong>on&nbsp;multiple effects, the enemy creature will only make 1 Save&nbsp;against all effects.</p>\n<p><strong>Save Fail: </strong>The target becomes&nbsp;<strong>Exposed </strong>(Attack&nbsp;Checks against it have ADV) against the next Attack Check&nbsp;made against it before the end of your next turn.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><em><strong>System Tip: </strong>You can add Attack Maneuvers as Weapon Enhacements for easier use. Just press \"Add Martial Maneuvers For Weapon\" on <strong>Enhancements </strong>tab on <strong>Item </strong>sheet.</em></p>",
